snippet.title: StairJump | Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
StairJump Launched for both android and ios!

Google Play : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Stairjump.StairsJump

App Store : https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id1302926417

Jump, fly, dodge - do not let the stairs take you down.
Jump high enough and you’ll achieve items, collect bonuses and coins.
The higher you’ll get, the better, but beware - not everyone wants your success, you’ll find new stairs and new enemies on your way up.

New jumpers are rising
Will you be the best?

More info:
http://stairjump.com/

Follow SUNFURY team for future updates:
http://sunfury.team/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/teamsunfury 
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/TeamSunfury/
